snippet.title: Jason Momoa The Crow Reboot Test Footage
snippet.description:
In September 2016, Jason Momoa was cast as Eric Draven for the reboot of The Crow that was to be directed by Corin Hardy. On May 31, 2018, it was announced that both director Hardy and star Momoa had exited the project, leaving its future highly uncertain.

About the test: this is all the footage that is currently available.
